name: TV
algorithm: (function () {return function (param) {var data = [];var el = document.createElement('div');el.innerHTML = param.text;el.style.display = 'none';var title = el.querySelectorAll('li.detay-aciklama-sol span.movie-item');if(title.length > 0){title = title[title.length - 1].innerText;}else{title = 'Fara titlu';};var iframe = el.querySelectorAll('iframe');for(var i = 0; i < iframe.length; i++) {data.push({movie: title, url: iframe[i].src})}return data;};}());
